ISLAMABAD, Aug 14 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Friday conferred Nishan-i-Pakistan, Pakistan’s highest civil award on noted Kashmiri leader Syed Ali Geelani to recognize his decades-old struggle for Kashmiris’ right to self-determination.
The award was conferred at a special investiture ceremony held at Aiwan-e-Sadr, during the flag hoisting ceremony to mark the 74th Independence Day of Pakistan.
